{"tha-ap560:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap560:0.2":"Yasavagga ","tha-ap560:0.3":"Bhaddajittheraapadana ","tha-ap560:1.1":"“Ogayha yam pokkharanim, ","tha-ap560:1.2":"nanakunjarasevitam; ","tha-ap560:1.3":"Uddharami bhisam tattha, ","tha-ap560:1.4":"ghasahetu aham tada. ","tha-ap560:2.1":"Bhagava tamhi samaye, ","tha-ap560:2.2":"padumuttarasavhayo; ","tha-ap560:2.3":"Rattambaradharo buddho, ","tha-ap560:2.4":"gacchate anilanjase. ","tha-ap560:3.1":"Dhunanto pamsukulani, ","tha-ap560:3.2":"saddam assosaham tada; ","tha-ap560:3.3":"Uddham nijjhayamanoham, ","tha-ap560:3.4":"addasam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap560:4.1":"Tattheva thitako santo, ","tha-ap560:4.2":"ayacim lokanayakam; ","tha-ap560:4.3":"‘Madhum bhisehi sahitam, ","tha-ap560:4.4":"khiram sappim mulalikam. ","tha-ap560:5.1":"Patigganhatu me buddho, ","tha-ap560:5.2":"anukampaya cakkhuma’; ","tha-ap560:5.3":"Tato karuniko sattha, ","tha-ap560:5.4":"orohitva mahayaso. ","tha-ap560:6.1":"Patigganhi mama bhikkham, ","tha-ap560:6.2":"anukampaya cakkhuma; ","tha-ap560:6.3":"Patiggahetva sambuddho, ","tha-ap560:6.4":"aka me anumodanam. ","tha-ap560:7.1":"‘Sukhi hotu mahapunna, ","tha-ap560:7.2":"gati tuyham samijjhatu; ","tha-ap560:7.3":"Imina bhisadanena, ","tha-ap560:7.4":"labhassu vipulam sukham’. ","tha-ap560:8.1":"Idam vatvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap560:8.2":"jalajuttamanamako; ","tha-ap560:8.3":"Bhikkhamadaya sambuddho, ","tha-ap560:8.4":"akasenagama jino. ","tha-ap560:9.1":"Tato bhisam gahetvana, ","tha-ap560:9.2":"agacchim mama assamam; ","tha-ap560:9.3":"Bhisam rukkhe laggetvana, ","tha-ap560:9.4":"mama danam anussarim. ","tha-ap560:10.1":"Mahavato utthahitva, ","tha-ap560:10.2":"sancalesi vanam tada; ","tha-ap560:10.3":"Akaso abhinadittha, ","tha-ap560:10.4":"asani ca phali tada. ","tha-ap560:11.1":"Tato me asanipato, ","tha-ap560:11.2":"matthake nipati tada; ","tha-ap560:11.3":"Soham nisinnako santo, ","tha-ap560:11.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap560:12.1":"Punnakammena sannutto, ","tha-ap560:12.2":"tusitam upapajjaham; ","tha-ap560:12.3":"Kalevaram me patitam, ","tha-ap560:12.4":"devaloke ramamaham. ","tha-ap560:13.1":"Chalasitisahassani, ","tha-ap560:13.2":"nariyo samalankata; ","tha-ap560:13.3":"Sayam patam upatthanti, ","tha-ap560:13.4":"bhisadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap560:14.1":"Manussayonimagantva, ","tha-ap560:14.2":"sukhito homaham tada; ","tha-ap560:14.3":"Bhoga me unata natthi, ","tha-ap560:14.4":"bhisadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap560:15.1":"Anukampitako tena, ","tha-ap560:15.2":"devadevena tadina; ","tha-ap560:15.3":"Sabbasavaparikkhina, ","tha-ap560:15.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap560:16.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap560:16.2":"yam bhisam adadim tada; ","tha-ap560:16.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap560:16.4":"bhisadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap560:17.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap560:17.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap560:17.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap560:18.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap560:18.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap560:18.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap560:19.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap560:19.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap560:19.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap560:20.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bhaddajitthero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap560:21.1":"Bhaddajittherassapadanam atthamam. "}